        {
            "+content": "Hiyori Hiwamura is a new high school teacher who just graduated from college. With Hiwamura's weak voice, weak stamina, and being basically weak in all aspects, one might have the urge to protect her. Ironically, students misinterpreted her meekness and feared her as the rumored \"Ms. Scary\" who would curse them if she got upset. Nevertheless, she works hard for her students, and one student, Akihito Abikura, recognizes her true nature.",
